  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate how QAX576 affects levels of interleukin 13
      (IL-13) in patients with idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis (IPF).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
