  </study_design_info>
  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>-To investigate the possibility that some IPF patients experience increased IL-13 production. Blood samples to be collected pre-dose and weekly after dosing. -To investigate the hypothesis that QAX576 will neutralize IL-13 in patients with IPF</measure>
    <time_frame>Week 1,2,3 and 4</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>-To evaluate the changes in biomarkers in blood over time in patients with IPF. Serum samples will be obtained at pre-dose and 2 weeks post-dose.</measure>
    <time_frame>Week 3</time_frame>
  </secondary_outcome>
